				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: gravestone of dire melodies<a name="25784"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 5 04 5:05 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Mez is not affected at all by wind instruments. Basically, the only thing affected by wind are the invis song and the Aria songs from LoY. I'd personally say that you shouldn't equip this, as it is very limited in use, and has a lower mod than the epic (I believe).
<br />

<br />

<br />
 Edit: Just thought that since you already have it, you might as well equip it until you have something else that you want to put in there (I think solvents cost like 20pp or something). I heard there is a way to turn in augs and get a fraction of the points back or something, but probably isn't even really worth it because the wind aug isn't very many points anyway.
<br />

<br />

<br />
    P.S. Wind instruments have nothing to do with Fading Memories.</span></td>
