				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: gravestone of dire melodies<a name="25814"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 5 04 6:30 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Wind instruments DO have an affect on how many counters are removed by Aria of Innocence and Aria of Asceticism -- the two heal songs we get in LOY.  In POP boss encounters or Luclin boss encounters, getting curse or disease counters stacked sky high is not uncommon.  The better wind multiplier you have, the more counters come off per pulse.  I realize this is a very situational thing, but it is one reason to have a wind augment tucked away somewhere in your armor.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
